<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFAFFFF1FAB2AE48815EFEA4" bold="true" box="[199,315,294,320]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Remarks.</emphasis>
Previous records from the coast of 
<collectingRegion id="AE158DE9FFAFFFF1F8B2AE48835DFEA4" box="[711,824,294,320]" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">São Paulo</collectingRegion>
